131
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:56,860
[SPEAKER_01] I ukrjeni malo tako čiti, meni provuklo to.

132
00:05:56,860 --> 00:06:03,480
[SPEAKER_01] Isus, stari zavijet, novi zavijet, kako to Isus, kako to sve.

133
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:07,079
[SPEAKER_01] A meni Isus to bilo moje bivše vjera.

134
00:06:07,079 --> 00:06:08,319
[SPEAKER_01] Isus bil prorok.

135
00:06:08,319 --> 00:06:11,660
[SPEAKER_01] Kav Mohamed, kav drugi.

136
00:06:11,660 --> 00:06:13,220
[SPEAKER_01] O, prorok.

137
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ukrjeni ja malo, razmislim ukrjeni malo razlikujeti.

138
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:25,100
[SPEAKER_01] I vidim u Koran, vidim u Biblije, čitam tamo, čitam u vamo.

139
00:06:25,100 --> 00:06:28,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ali bili meni uvijek, da somljiv.

140
